<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Insert title here</title>
</head>
<body>
<h1>컨트롤러에서 보낸 리스트 출력, 인라인 방식으로</h1>
	<h2>[[${list}]]</h2>
	<hr>
	<h2 th:text="${list}"></h2>
	
	<!-- th:each 사용 -->
	<ul>
	<li th:each="str:${list}" th:text="${str}"></li>
	</ul>
	
	<hr>
	<ul>
	<li th:each="str:${list}">[[${str}]]</li>
	</ul>
	
	<hr>
	<ul>
	<th:block th:each="str:${list}">
		<li>[[${str}]]</li>
	</th:block>
	</ul>
	
	<hr>
	<ul>
		<li th:each="str, status:${list}">
			[[${status.count}]] - [[${str}]]
		</li>
	</ul>
	
	<ul>
		<li th:each="str, status:${list}">
			[[${status.index}]] - [[${str}]]
		</li>
	</ul>
	
		<ul>
		<li th:each="str, status:${list}">
			[[${status.size}]] - [[${str}]]
		</li>
	</ul>
	
	<hr>
		<ul>
			<li th:each="str, status:${list}">
			<span th:if="${status.odd}">ODD--[[${str}]]</span>
			<span th:unless="${status.odd}">ENEN--[[${str}]]</span>
			</li>
		</ul>	
		
		<ul>
			<li th:each="str, status:${list}">
				<span th:text="${status.odd} ? 'ODD ---'+${str} : 'EVEN ---'+${str}"></span>
			</li>
		</ul>	
		
		<hr>
		<ul>
		<li th:each="str, status:${list}">
			<th:block th:switch="${status.index%3}">
				<span th:case="0">0--[[${str}]]</span>
				<span th:case="1">1--[[${str}]]</span>
				<span th:case="2">2--[[${str}]]</span>
			</th:block>
		</li>
		</ul>		
		
		<hr>
		<a th:href="@{/hello}">GO TO /hello</a>
		<a th:href="@{/hello(name='aaa',age='20')}">GO TO /hello</a>
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
</body>
</html>